  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à WebKitGTK</title>

    <para>
      The <application>WebKitGTK</application> package is a port of the portable
web rendering engine <application>WebKit</application> to the
<application>GTK+ 3</application> and <application>GTK 4</application>
platforms.
    </para>

    &lfs112_checked;

